N/A
Title: Flight Test                                                                                                                          3.372       5.215          5.569
Description: Contractor Flight Test support to continue contractor testing of new capabilities as required. Costs include but not
limited to maintenance on test aircraft, contractor engineering support for test related technical and safety of flight issues, test
planning, test analysis, and support of test execution. It also includes Edwards AFB Flight Test Support where direct costs are
related to flight testing and include ramp space, fuel, air traffic control, range costs, etc., which are items each weapon system
must pay when using Air Force flight test locations.

FY 2026 Plans:
Flight test support for related technical and safety of flight issues, test planning, and test analysis activities.
