Title: Databus Collection & Analytics (DBCA)                                                                                                2.500       0.000          0.000
Description: Databus Collection and Analytics (DBCA), previously Databus Reporting System (DBRS),
has been renamed to highlight both the hardware and analytics capabilities instead of focusing primarily on
hardware. DBCA will capture and apply analytics to all data present across all databuses on the C-17 aircraft
to provide and drive efficiencies in predictive maintenance, operations, training, safety considerations and
cybersecurity concerns. This comprehensive aircraft data collection system will record, transfer and retain,
process and analyze, and provide aircraft and fleet recommendations. Data analysis to be comprehensive
enough to forecast/trend root-cause analysis, drive predictive maintenance decisions, accomplish propulsion/
APU health trending programs, and provide sortie reconstruction for operator training/debriefing.

