FY 2025 Plans:
Continue developing space-based solar power collection and transmission technology via a series of integrated demos and
technology development/maturation efforts: 1) continue space flight demonstration of solar-to-RF panel payload (take delivery
of solar-to-RF payload emulator, validate payload for delivery, continue pre-integration of payload-to-bus), 2) deliver thermal
