E. Acquisition Strategy
C/KC-135 MUOS acquisition strategy addresses cryptographic modernization mandates and DoW directives by executing a 39-month Sole Source, Cost Plus Fixed
Fee EMD contract followed by a three-year production and installation effort. Major Events/ Milestone: Prototype install on Aircraft Number 1 April 15th, 2025 - April
25th, 2025, Prototype install on Aircraft Number 2 April 26th, 2025 - May 3rd, 2025, Combined DT/OT Effort May 3rd, 2025 - October 19th, 2025, Black Label Release
December 9, 2025, Milestone C April, 2026, Installation Q1 of FY 2027 - Q1 of FY 2030. Current as of 9 December 2025.

